cess fails with `InaccessibleObjectException`. Normal `ObjectMapper` serialization/deserialization tests using the shaded `shaded.parquet.com.fasterxml.jackson.*` APIs do not require additional dependencies or Docker.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The reported failure appears to be a version-behavior drift in a direct `JacksonAnnotationIntrospector.findEnumValue` assertion, not missing setup.\",\n    \"Tests should avoid depending on deprecated/internal Jackson behavior that changed between the shaded Jackson versions bundled by Parquet 1.12.2 and 1.16.0.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_04f3de4735fb2ae1016a3fc3b383d48194bb5dad41c101a012\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1198, "output": 775, "cacheRead": 31232, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33205, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782563753035, "responseId": "resp_04f3de4735fb2ae1016a3fc3a9a8d08194bc3a676532633d17"}}
